---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Najbolji IPTV provajderi 2025 - EXYU IPTV" description="Pregled najboljih IPTV provajdera i naša preporuka za 2025. godinu.">
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>Natrag na blog</a>
        <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Preporuke</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-4 mb-6">Najbolji IPTV provajderi u 2025</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-500 mb-8"><span>22.02.2025</span><span>•</span><span>5 min čitanja</span></div>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Koji IPTV provajder je najbolji u 2025? Pročitajte naš pregled i preporuke.</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-12 mb-4">Kako ocjenjujemo provajdere?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-8">
            <li>Broj kanala i kvalitet</li>
            <li>Stabilnost usluge</li>
            <li>Korisnička podrška</li>
            <li>Cijena</li>
            <li>Jednostavnost korištenja</li>
          </ul>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-12 mb-4">Naša preporuka</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">EXYU IPTV nudi najbolji odnos cijene i kvalitete za balkansku dijasporu.</p>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-8">
            <a href="/osnovni-paket" class="btn btn-primary">Pogledajte ponudu</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
